Package client

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Client
    Client.java Purpose : Server-Client Log Controller program Client side to run Client.
    Config
    Configuration class, which take care of json file from Client side, it take all parameters and prepares them for further use Config.java
    File
    File class is used to create a file from given path in configuration file.
    FileProcessing
    Client side one of the most important classes, it will create a File object, pass it to WatcherThread, starts the threading and stores it in variable array FileProcessing.java
    ServerComm
    Server communication class allowing Client communicate with Server through sockets
    WatcherThread
    Thread which will look for changed date on file
